extendedInfo.description: Fetch My Droid Version: 2.0.0Formerly Fetch It - added locating feature -removed donations and paid app version\n\r\nWhen you have lost your phone in the house and your ringer is on vibrate or on low volume, text the string (fetch it) or another string to your phone. The ringer will turn on and be set to maximum volume until you have found your phone.  ***NEW*** If you lost your phone across town or the world, you can locate it! Enjoy!
